{"tid":1107795,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大戶如果齊心聯手做沽空(Short sell)  ， 係咪100% 賺錢？","createTime":"2019-04-15T13:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T15:17:28.000Z","uid":123335,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d78639c2580f36241adaf5bbef1a05fea8dad4c2","tid":1107795,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"假設某股票現價 $100 <br />\n大戶齊心聯手做沽空<br />\n由於大量出貨, 市場 Supply 突然供應過大, 個股價會暴跌<br />\n呢個時候，散戶有兩種，不過兩種都會淆底跟風走貨止蝕：<br />\n1）感覺型散戶：見個價跌咁多，再睇埋d 嚇鬼既新聞，嚇到鼻哥窿都冇肉，拿拿林止蝕走貨 <br />\n2）技術分析型散戶：股價跌咁多，一定跌穿10天20天線，MACD 又會下穿信號線，所以會理性地止蝕出貨 <br />\n<br />\n當個價暴跌到$80 左右 <br />\n大戶覺得夠皮了，就用返$80 買貨入市完成整個沽空過程<br />\n輕輕鬆鬆就賺左$20差價既利潤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢個方法係咪100% work <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s. 窮撚散戶ff中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62f481e80a84be2812e545aef9fb5ee141af64e","tid":1107795,"uid":4942,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:26:33.000Z","msg":"理論上可行但實際上人性貪婪<br />\n<br />\n只會想自己賺最多<br />\n<br />\n結果...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53c6e4e56db3d3278457b134020078fa1861165","tid":1107795,"uid":227275,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:28:41.000Z","msg":"講咁多做乜 不嬲都大戶玩晒"},{"pid":"6996e849bf1ac26a84eaed37e37d30fbdc608554","tid":1107795,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f62f481e80a84be2812e545aef9fb5ee141af64e","tid":1107795,"uid":4942,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:26:33.000Z","msg":"理論上可行但實際上人性貪婪<br />\n<br />\n只會想自己賺最多<br />\n<br />\n結果...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"想聽多少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21d64df917d69fac26f8ba3f99a6ab3fc9d6